message.text:
look! i made itttt! 🤗

from a simple freshie entering thy happy halls without knowing what amazing things will happen to me in an instant. from executive commiteee of pubcon and  becoming its director, and now being an associate director marcon gives me a lot of goosebumps as i still do not believe it. 

maybe that little fear whether to pursue an org for your college journey can be your next big thing. everything starts with progress and confidence, kayang kaya 'yan mapadama ni marcon for you 😉

if you like caption making, content creation, video contents script making, disseminating information to the tamaraws real time (tamanunsyo kween), then this is your sign! marketing and content department will lead you to rise and stick with you together 💖

🔗 https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm

cc Kiel Pearnicole Sharlene Abby

cc Kiel Pearnicole Sharlene Abby
